2008.10.29
* Modified yaffs2 utils mkyaffs2image to support writting 4KB pagesize NAND. NAND layout 
  is (0 - raw(512B pagesize), 1 - nand_oob_64(2KB pagesize), 2 - nand_oob_128(4KB pagesize)). 
  <lhhuang@ingenic.cn>
  Updated file:
      fs/yaffs2/utils/mkyaffs2image.c

